    <item>
      <title>全球顶级银行认为中国难以实现 5% 的增长目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/top-global-banks-see-china-struggling-to-hit-5-growth-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[目前，绝大多数全球银行预计今年中国经济增速将低于 5%，其中美国银行公司 (Bank of America Corp.) 是最新一家下调预测的银行，与高盛集团 (Goldman Sachs Group Inc.) 和摩根大通 (JPMorgan Chase &amp; Co.) 等银行一样。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/top-global-banks-see-china-struggling-to-hit-5-growth-target</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 06:38:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中非合作峰会在北京开幕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-04/china-africa-cooperation-summit-begins-n-beijing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲领导人抵达北京参加第九届中非合作论坛。这是自 2018 年以来在北京举行的首次此类峰会，也是习近平今年主持的最大外交活动。彭博新闻社的 Ondiro Oganga 与 Joumanna Bercetche 就“中东和非洲视野”进行了讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-04/china-africa-cooperation-summit-begins-n-beijing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 06:35:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通成立迪拜私人银行团队，助力财富热潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/dubai-wealth-boom-jpmorgan-jpm-sets-up-private-banking-team-in-city</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通公司正在迪拜组建一个私人银行团队，加入众多竞争对手的行列，这些竞争对手已将更多资源部署到中东，希望利用涌入该地区的数千名百万富翁的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/dubai-wealth-boom-jpmorgan-jpm-sets-up-private-banking-team-in-city</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 06:26:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球经济担忧导致欧洲股市科技股下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/european-stock-futures-drop-on-us-economy-fears-before-jobs-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对全球经济健康状况的担忧削弱了本周晚些时候美国关键就业数据公布前的市场人气，欧洲股市下跌。科技股下跌，追随 Nvidia Corp. 隔夜下跌的脚步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/european-stock-futures-drop-on-us-economy-fears-before-jobs-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 05:46:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
